X^*
f_k(x)=c_k\mathrm e^{-u_k(x)}
c_k\to\frac1{\sqrt{2\pi}}
u_k(x)\to\frac12x^2
k\to\infty
 c_k=\frac{\mathrm e^{-k}k^{k-1/2}}{\Gamma(k)},\qquad u_k(x)=k(\mathrm e^{x/\sqrt{k}}-1)-\sqrt{k}x, 
